    "Html": "<p id=afe69b80-f225-012c-12b1-1231390c3961>Hi James,</p>\r\n<p id=afe6a8e0-f225-012c-12b2-1231390c3961>As you said, you need to <a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd458901.aspx\">create a new RegionAdapter</a> to be able to modify the item&rsquo;s style. Take into account that as there is already an adapter for the <strong>ItemsControl</strong>, you could inherit from it and add the required functionality.</p>\r\n<p id=afe6b6d0-f225-012c-12b3-1231390c3961>Please let me know if this helps.</p>\r\n<p id=afe6c460-f225-012c-12b4-1231390c3961>Damian Schenkelman    <br><a href=\"http://blogs.southworks.net/dschenkelman\">http://blogs.southworks.net/dschenkelman</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
